title: Ci Han Vegetarian Restaurant
description: Buddhist vegetarian restaurant with a conscientious staff who is able to communicate in English. The restaurant is air-conditioned and has a cozy ambiance. The spread includes single dishes such as fried noodles or rice in various styles, and white rice with side dishes (e.g. tofu hotplate, oatmeal shrimp, vegetable stir-fry and many more). May include some MSG (not entirely sure) - ask.
